com.indooratlas.android

Class ErrorCodes

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.indooratlas.android.ErrorCodes

  • public class ErrorCodes
extends java.lang.Object
    ErrorCodes class contains the error codes used in service failures. Error code groups: 1000-1099 Device errors 2000-2099 Connection errors / technical errors from service. 3000-3099 Content errors / permission errors from service. 4000-4100 Backend errors / errors related to accessing data from service.
    Since:
    0.5
